T1  - The Concept of “Coalition” in Organization Theory and Research
AU  - Stevenson, William B.
AU  - Pearce, Jone L.
AU  - Porter, Lyman W.
Y1  - 1985/04/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1985.4278178
